OL,5, The government has said it is prepared 
OL,6, for a "range of scenarios" following   
OL,7, reports that Thames Water could be on  
OL,8, the brink of collapse.                 
OL,10,FMinisters declined to comment on the   
OL,11,Fcompany's situation, but said regulator
OL,12,FOfwat monitored "the financial         
OL,13,Fposition" of all water firms.          
OL,15,FThames Water has been under pressure   
OL,16,Fover its performance and is reportedly 
OL,17,Fstruggling under a #14bn debt pile.    
OL,19,FThe business is yet to comment on the  
OL,20,Fspeculation over its future.           
